</td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.nuclearspace.com/ezboard/images/posticons/16.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Nuclear thermal rocket accidents.</span><hr size=1> I don't believe that there are any natural fissile materials.  Pu-239 and U-235 are both man-made.<br>
